      <title>欧盟制裁卢旺达军事官员对刚果冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/rwanda-severs-diplomatic-relations-with-belgium</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，欧洲联盟批准了三名卢旺达军事官员和一家金炼油厂，因为批评基加利对M23民兵的支持在数十年来的最新冲突中占领了刚果东部民主共和国东部民主共和国的两个主要城市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/rwanda-severs-diplomatic-relations-with-belgium</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 11:19:56 GMT</pubDate>
